5. 综合裁决：发放闸门输出（MUST）🚦
payout_gate_status ∈ {PAYOUT_ALLOWED, PAYOUT_DELAYED, PAYOUT_BLOCKED}

最小规则（MUST）：
- 若 STAGE1_FAILED 或 STAGE2_FAILED → PAYOUT_BLOCKED
- 若存在 NEEDS_HUMAN / UNCLEAR / ANOMALY 未闭环 → PAYOUT_DELAYED
- 仅当 STAGE1_PASSED 且 STAGE2_PASSED 且无 Dispute/Hold/AuditOpen 阻断 → PAYOUT_ALLOWED

